        public BlastHitHspImplem(SRHit hit,
                 String bc,
                 int hspNum,
                 int qSize,
                 int bType)
        Creates a BlastHitHsp.
        Parameters:
        hit - the hit containing the HSP to display
        bc - the BlastClient that produced this BlastHitHsp
        hspNum - the HSP to display, identified by its order number within the Hit
        qSize - the query size
        bType - the Blast type, one of SROutput.BLASTXXX integer constants
